author: COMSOL
description: This example, which shows how to analyze failure from deformations near an open-hole well, comes from Dr. Roberto Suarez Rivera of TerraTek Inc. Their poroelastic approach builds a model of porous media flow with solid deformation and analyzes the potential for collapse using Coulomb failure expressions.
